# Static archive of GameCon 2000 (reconstructed from the Internet Archive).
#
# GameCon 2000 ran 13.-16.7.2000 in OLOMOUC (DDM, třída 17. listopadu 47). It
# was a SECTION of the whole altar.cz publisher site (path altar.cz/gamecon/),
# the same path-era as 1998-1999/2001-2005 — older than the gamecon.altar.cz
# subdomain (2006-2008).
#
# IMPORTANT — this is a MINIMAL, honest archive. Wayback never preserved a
# distinct GameCon 2000 HOMEPAGE separate from the rolling Altar section. What
# genuinely survives, and is served here:
#   - the Mistrovství v DrD + tournament RESULTS: vysledky00 (real 2000 results,
#     from a 2001 capture) + vysledky98/99,
#   - a period-correct Altar-layout homepage with the genuine 2000 festival
#     recap (date + Olomouc DDM venue + the captured "mapka" venue map),
#     pointing at the 2000 results and previous years.
# The 2000 program/tournament pages were never published/captured — they 404.
#
# Pages restored from web.archive.org, transcoded WINDOWS-1250 -> UTF-8 (with an
# injected <meta charset>; the source declared charset only via the HTTP header).
# Dead ad embeds (Mr.Lin(x), billboard.cz) stripped. Dynamic CGI -> themed 404.

DirectoryIndex index.html
ErrorDocument 404 /404.html

Options -Indexes

<IfModule mod_rewrite.c>
    RewriteEngine On

    RewriteCond %{REQUEST_FILENAME} -f
    RewriteRule ^ - [L]

    RewriteCond %{REQUEST_FILENAME} -d
    RewriteCond %{REQUEST_FILENAME}/index.html -f
    RewriteRule ^ - [L]

    RewriteRule ^$  index.html [L]

    RewriteRule ^.*$ - [R=404,L]
</IfModule>
